<h1>The Hidden Cost of Landing Page Builders: Why $15/Month Costs You $2,400/Year</h1>
<p class="subtitle">We compared the real annual cost of every major landing page builder. The results will change how you think about your next landing page.</p>
<div class="meta">Published May 8, 2026 · 8 min read · Pricing data verified from official websites</div>

<p>You need a landing page. You Google "best landing page builder" and find Carrd ($19/year), Typedream (free), Dorik (free), Framer (free). Great, right? Free or cheap.</p>

<p>But here's what those pricing pages don't tell you: <strong>the annual cost of "cheap" landing page builders ranges from $199 to $2,400 per year</strong>. And you don't own anything.</p>

