<h2>FAQ</h2>

<h3>Is this really cheaper than Carrd?</h3>
<p>Carrd Pro Lite is $19/year, which seems cheaper than $29. But Carrd only lets you build ONE page, and you don't own the code. Over 3 years, Carrd costs $57 and you still don't own anything. ZOO costs $29 once and you own the files forever.</p>

<h3>What about Typedream's free plan?</h3>
<p>Typedream's free plan is extremely limited — no custom domain, Typedream branding, limited pages. To get a professional landing page, you need at least the Launch plan ($15/month = $180/year).</p>

<h3>Do I need to know code?</h3>
<p>Basic HTML/CSS knowledge helps but isn't required. Our templates are well-commented and easy to customize. If you can edit a text file, you can customize these templates.</p>

<h3>Can I use these for client projects?</h3>
<p>Yes. One license covers unlimited personal and commercial projects. Build landing pages for yourself or your clients.</p>

